snippet.title: Irwin Ego Ace Attorney: Turnabout Hospitality WIP Showcase
snippet.description:
Link to Irwin Ego if you would like to play it for yourself:
https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1L4eKzTMeB2Vc-OkM9LSORDHw4dFvmrdp?usp=share_link

You will need to download PyWright in order to play it, though.
To download PyWright, please follow this link: http://pywright.dawnsoft.org/

I will only continue production on Irwin Ego IF enough people want to see it. If you would like to see this finished, please let me know in the comments. Thank you.
